earlyseptember car sales and a 305 percent rise in truck sales for 
a vehicle sales rate 108 percent higher during the period this year 
than last year 
so far this year gm reported its car and truck sales were 46 
percent behind last years 
chryslers earlyseptember vehicle sales were mixed with car 
sales rising 67 percent and truck sales falling 83 percent 
combined chryslers vehicle sales were 06 percent below the 
earlyseptember rate last year 
chrysler car and truck sales through sept 10 of this year were 
61 percent behind last years rate 
