year to clear the way for a new sportutility truck 
escorts and tracers will be made in the detroit suburb of wayne 
and in hermosillo mexico where they currently are assembled 
company executives said wednesday the escort plant in edison nj 
will be switched to making ranger light pickup trucks which now are 
assembled in louisville ky 
